snippet.title: Wildcard | Announcement Trailer (2022)
snippet.description:
Wildcard is a first-of-its-kind hybrid of real-time strategy, arena-based MOBAs, and collectible card games, all powered by the blockchain. Witness the pulse-pounding mix of action and strategy in the pre-alpha trailer.

Learn more at https://www.wildcardgame.com/
